-- UniCredit Is Said to Hire Banks to Sell Tier 1 Bonds Denominated in Euros
-- Caroline Hyde
-- 2010-07-13T07:38:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/unicredit-is-said-to-hire-banks-to-sell-tier-1-bonds-denominated-in-euros.html

          
          
             UniCredit SpA plans to sell Tier 1
bonds in euros, according to two people with knoweldge of the
transaction.  
 Credit Suisse Group AG and JPMorgan Chase & Co. will manage
the sale with UniCredit, the people said.  
          
          


  


        